            ],
            [
                "As I open my eyes, I realize it’s just another day."
            ],
            [
                "I swear I could hear my bed call out to me to go back to sleep as I stretch out of it with"
            ],
            [
                "all the calmness in the world."
            ],
            [
                "I then look at the clock, and sigh in relief as It barely was 10 am, not too late but not quite early either."
            ],
            [
                "This day felt like a very chill one, with nothing to do really… but that just can’t be right."
            ],
            [
                "I always have something to do."
            ],
            [
                "I call out for Helpie, but all I’m met with is silence…"
            ],
            [
                " which is even weirder."
            ],
            [
                "Ever since my grandma gifted me the Help13 robot"
            ],
            [
                "(Or Helpie, as I decided to name them), "
            ],
            [
                "they've always been with me, helping me with my chores, prepping my meals,"
            ],
            [
                "and of course, being a friend to me…"
            ],
            [
                "I get up and hurriedly dress up to go and search for my robot. If Helpie is not home, something must be very off."
            ]
        ],
